OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773004305
OL,3,C17-year-old boy arrested for death
OL,4,Cthreats which forced school into
OL,5,Clockdown
OL,7,FA 17-year-old boy from Pontardawe has
OL,8,Fbeen arrested after allegedly sending
OL,9,Fthreats relating to death or serious
OL,10,Fharm, which forced a Powys school into
OL,11,Flockdown earlier this week.
OL,13,FDyfed-Powys Police were called to
OL,14,FMaesydderwen Comprehensive School in
OL,15,FYstradgynlais at around 10:45 on
OL,16,FMonday 2 March.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
