OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773004305
OL,3,C17-year-old boy arrested for death
OL,4,Cthreats which forced school into
OL,5,Clockdown
OL,7,FThe force says the boy has been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of sending
OL,9,Fdigital communications conveying
OL,10,Fthreats of death or serious harm, with
OL,11,Fthe intent to cause fear.
OL,13,FThey add that he remains in police
OL,14,Fcustody.
OL,16,FThe school was closed throughout
OL,17,FTuesday 3 March whilst police
OL,18,Fcontinued their enquiries but reopened
OL,19,Fa day later after a safety review was
OL,20,Fcarried out which deemed pupils were
OL,21,Fsafe to return to school.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
