PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773004305
OL,3,C17-year-old boy arrested for death
OL,4,Cthreats which forced school into
OL,5,Clockdown
OL,7,FPowys Superintendent Gareth Grant,
OL,8,Fsaid, "I'd firstly like to thank the
OL,9,Fparents, teachers, staff and the wider
OL,10,Fcommunity, for the support and
OL,11,Fpatience you have shown whilst we have
OL,12,Fcarried out our enquiries in relation
OL,13,Fto this incident.
