OL,3,C17-year-old boy arrested for death
OL,4,Cthreats which forced school into
OL,5,Clockdown
OL,7,F"I understand this will have had a
OL,8,Fprofound impact. Our Neighbourhood
OL,9,Fofficers will maintain a local
OL,10,Fpresence for reassurance, and we will
OL,11,Fcontinue to work with our local
OL,12,Fsecondary schools, and partners, to
OL,13,Fensure our local community are
OL,14,Fsupported."
